headline: GoDaddy Brings Agentic AI to Small Businesses with Launch of Airo.ai
summary: GoDaddy today launched Airo.ai, a Beta agentic artificial intelligence (AI) website and experience that turns a simple conversation into completed tasks for small businesses.
